[size=5][b]Filter Tabs[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][b]Favourites[/b] — Games you've starred as favourites (includes hidden favourites)
[*][b]All Games[/b] — All auto-detected and manually added games
[*][b]Installed[/b] — Games with at least one component installed
[*][b]Not Installed[/b] — Games with no components installed
